                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.811/998: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Shanghai</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lockhart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-06-29T15:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 29, 1938—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>407. Your 900, June 25, 10 a.m., Whangpoo Conservancy Board. The Department
                    authorizes you to associate yourself with your other interested colleagues in
                    recommending a settlement of the controversy as suggested in paragraph 2 of your
                    telegram under reference.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
